      rotate: -7,
      x: "6%",
      y: "16%",
      quote:
        "Lunemint helped my school project look so polished. I loved the bright style and fast turnaround.",
      alias: "— Maya, presentation client",
    },
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: -8,
      x: "34%",
      y: "24%",
      quote:
        "The brand cards are chic and easy to edit. Every slide felt custom and full of personality.",
      alias: "— Asha, social media client",
    },
    {
      tag: "blue",
      rotate: 8,
      x: "72%",
      y: "20%",
      quote:
        "I got a lovely stack of graphics that match my page. The final result was cleaner than expected.",
      alias: "— Ren, business client",
    },
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: 10,
      x: "10%",
      y: "62%",
      quote:
        "My presentation felt professional and fun. The design made the content really pop.",
      alias: "— Toni, pitch deck client",
    },
    {
      tag: "blue",
      rotate: 7,
      x: "44%",
      y: "68%",
      quote:
        "They delivered a beautiful patterned set with strong color and layout balance.",
      alias: "— Sia, branding client",
    },
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: -10,
      x: "76%",
      y: "62%",
      quote:
        "The resume template was crisp and easy to customize. It really stood out to recruiters.",
      alias: "— Jay, career client",
    },
  ],
  [
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: -6,
      x: "6%",
      y: "18%",
      quote:
        "The content felt polished and the layout was exactly what my project needed.",
      alias: "— Zara, creative client",
    },
    {
      tag: "blue",
      rotate: -9,
      x: "34%",
      y: "26%",
      quote:
        "I loved how easy the templates were to personalize, and the colors were so eye-catching.",
      alias: "— Nia, event client",
    },
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: 9,
      x: "72%",
      y: "18%",
      quote:
        "The new look made my brand feel cohesive and stylish. It was exactly what I wanted.",
      alias: "— Kira, brand client",
    },
    {
      tag: "blue",
      rotate: 10,
      x: "12%",
      y: "58%",
      quote:
        "The designs were creative and easy to use. I got lots of compliments from my team.",
      alias: "— Sam, digital client",
    },
    {
      tag: "purple",
      rotate: 6,
      x: "44%",
      y: "66%",
      quote:
        "The final graphics felt custom and professional without overcomplicating things.",
      alias: "— Emi, marketing client",
    },
    {
      tag: "blue",
      rotate: -8,
      x: "76%",
      y: "60%",
      quote:
